 <fr:p>We use the fact that the additive operation of the boolean semiring is disjunction and the multiplicative operation is conjunction:</fr:p>

 <fr:tex
display="block">    \begin {aligned}     { \mathopen {} \left ( N \cdot  M \right ) \mathclose {}} _{i,j} &amp;=  \bigoplus _{k \in { \mathopen {} \left  [ m \right  ] \mathclose {}} } M_{i,k} \cdot  N_{k,j}     \\     &amp;=     \bigvee _{k \in { \mathopen {} \left  [ m \right  ] \mathclose {}} } M_{i,k} \land  N_{k,j}     \\     &amp;=     \exists  k \in { \mathopen {} \left  [ m \right  ] \mathclose {}} \mathpunct {.}     M_{i,k} \land  N_{k,j}    \end {aligned}  </fr:tex>
